HEADWORD: Patronizing
<hw>Pa"tron*i`zing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Showing
condescending favor; assuming the manner of airs of a superior toward
another.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Pat"ron*i`zing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<au>Thackeray.</au></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

